game.name: Darts Pro Multiplayer
game.description:
Wow! You have brought to you a brand new sports challenge where you can sharpen your darts skills. Would you like to accept this challenge and show off the world that nobody can beat you in darting? Join Darts Pro Multiplayer and be prepared to practice your dart abilities in the best online platform you have ever witnessed! Choose from mode out of the three options multiplayer, play against the PC or challenge your friend playing on the same device in this brand new sports game!

Look at the most common official rules of the Darts Regulation Authority and then enter and make your win in this HTML5 dart game! It is up to you which option you want to choose from. Play alone or compete against an AI or a human player multiplayer! Select your throwing position and strength wisely to hit the maximum points every time with the help of darts available at your hand! Track your score at the top left corner of the screen!

You can also see how many darts available at your hand by looking at the top bottom of the screen. Click the screen to aim your target and then release it by setting your power bar in this classic Olympic sports game! We cover many top liked and popular free arcade games that are free to play online without download. Choose your favorite game and get ready to beat your boring hours while having quality fun and entertainment without download! Good luck to become the master of dart!
